{"tid":1461626,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 自己的文宣自己做（基礎）","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:22:45.000Z","uid":139173,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c99717851e0b14484ca79a1367dc3e224049fb7","tid":1461626,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1Ye5VY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1Ye5VY.jpg&h=edf08865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1．前言</span></span></strong><br />\n(上個post眼殘打錯字，感謝細心巴打提醒) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本人係連登第二次出文。我只係一人團隊，好多野都考慮不周。有好多熱心巴絲想整文宣但無咩概念，所以我整左個基礎心得分享，同埋template 連用法(詳見最底)， 比大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2．概念</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">＝2a：讀者＝</span></strong><br />\n首先，做文宣要搞清楚 <strong>讀者係邊個</strong> ，呢樣野完全影響文宣內容。例如「警察」，比巴絲睇你可以叫「克警」；比藍絲中立派要用「失控警員」。文宣一定令讀者放低介心，先可以做到宣傳效果，否則你後面幾天花龍鳳，對唔住都係圍爐晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">＝2b：材料＝</span></strong><br />\n文宣四寶：紙、圖、標題、內容 （同連登開post一樣）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／紙／</span></strong><br />\n貼牆愈大愈好，可以考慮4張a4合做1張a3。派街唔好太大張，可以考慮b5／半張a4<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／圖／</span></strong><br />\n請誇張清楚，必要時可以用指嘴，圈圈等方式 <strong>標示重點</strong> 。同時可以加上一句簡單caption描述一下張圖講咩。經費許可請彩print ＞用highlight pen＞黑白。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／標題／</span></strong><br />\n請放 <strong>最多時間思考一個好標題</strong> 。標題要交待發生事件，同埋得出結論。舉例義士爆眼單野，要交待警察使用過度暴力，結論得出政府警察正仆街。<br />\n<br />\n第一版<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>「失控警察實彈爆眼；女示威者永久失明」</em></span><br />\n＃失控 (降低警方威信) ＃實彈爆眼 (暴力) ＃女示威者永久失明 (事件及嚇人結果)<br />\n<br />\n最終版<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>「失控警察濫用私刑；實彈槍瞄頭爆眼」</em></span><br />\n＃失控 (降低警方威信) ＃濫用私刑 (暴力) ＃實彈槍瞄頭爆眼(流暢動作交待事件)<br />\n<br />\n我故意刪走女示威者，避免藍絲中立派先入為主：<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>先有示威者生事＞警察合理開槍＞示威者自作自受＞所以抵死</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／內容／</span></strong><br />\n內容都要交待更多細節，最後一定要有一個 <strong>你要帶出既message </strong>。<br />\n<br />\n例如義士爆眼單野：<br />\n「香港政府縱容警方無視工作指示，濫用暴力，嚴重違反專業操守」<br />\n<br />\n整張文宣要令藍絲中立派睇完 <strong>質疑政府處理失當，警方失職</strong>  。唔好期望佢地一下子轉槍頭屌政府，只要令藍絲中立派同情示威者，開始質疑佢地眼中全能既政府，文宣已經成功達成任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住我地要政府係藍絲中立派心中失信，咁我地表達訴求就會少左好多社區阻力。<br />\n<br />\n注：以上用左藍絲中立派文宣做例。我好欣賞其他海報文宣巴絲，自己未有咁既能力同時間，但好支持你地用靚poster團結我地，係到講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3．其他</span>[/maroon]</strong><br />\n－藍絲中立派睇既文宣字一定要大隻，佢地對眼係自動過濾細字<br />\n－機場遊客文宣一定要有英文<br />\n－（有待大家補充）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[purple]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4．工具</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">＝4a：我做既Templat＝</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8OfpJNk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8OfpJNk.jpg&h=7cc8c2ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoyVQsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoyVQsm.jpg&h=124d9dd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／google drive下載／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yDl9fQkyd-SxD0KTFf-hodabcFGvaVc0/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1yDl9fQkyd-SxD0KTFf-hodabcFGvaVc0%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=c00ad00e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yDl9fQkyd-SxD0KTFf-hodabcFGvaVc0/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">＝4b：編輯加字工具＝</span></strong><br />\n可用AI、PS、Indesign、小畫家、等工具、even手畫<br />\n 亦可用以下online PS (呢個試過打到中文）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／Online_Photoshop／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.onlinephotoshopfree.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlinephotoshopfree.info%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=d91788ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.onlinephotoshopfree.info/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">／我做既教學／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nDBYkvATApg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnDBYkvATApg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=1fe79718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nDBYkvATApg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n＃香港加油 ＃不分化不割蓆不篤灰 ＃五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf5945929dbb9b887a78d7f4c5585cd6d655e89","tid":1461626,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"全民親善大使月 正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n輕輕推一下"},{"pid":"9d1d9f1bff70a2b37d74b2efd554830087ac3f2a","tid":1461626,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"848c3e859fa9f92c3b00877183d16295951387e5","tid":14